### Archivo para pruebas HTTP de tus endpoints API
# Cambia la URL base si usas otro puerto o dominio
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Auth
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nuevo@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nuevo@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "name": "Nuevo Usuario"
}

### NextAuth Session
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/session

